Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.model

Class ContentModelFactory

java.lang.Object
chav1961.purelib.model.ContentModelFactory
public class ContentModelFactory
extends java.lang.Object

THis class is a factory for most model sources. It can load models from external sources or build models by existent entities.

Since:
0.0.3
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
LastUpdate:

    • forAnnotatedClass

      public static ContentMetadataInterface forAnnotatedClass​(java.lang.Class<?> clazz) throws java.lang.NullPointerException, java.lang.IllegalArgumentException, LocalizationException, ContentException

      Build model for annotated class. Class to build model for must be annotated with LocaleResourceLocation and LocaleResource annotations, and some of it's fields must be annotated with LocaleResource and/or Format annotations

      Parameters:
      clazz - class to build model for
      Returns:
      model built. Can't be null
      Throws:
      java.lang.NullPointerException - class to build model for is null
      java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - come mandatory annotations are missing in the class
      LocalizationException - on any localization exceptions
      ContentException - on any format errors

    • forOrdinalClass

      public static ContentMetadataInterface forOrdinalClass​(java.lang.Class<?> clazz) throws java.lang.NullPointerException, java.lang.IllegalArgumentException, LocalizationException, ContentException

      Build model for ordinal class. Differ to forAnnotatedClass(Class) method, this model is reduced and contains field descriptors only. Localizer for the given model will be associated to PureLib localizer, all labels in the model will be replaced with model names.

      Parameters:
      clazz - class to build model for
      Returns:
      model built. Can't be null
      Throws:
      java.lang.NullPointerException - class to build model for is null
      java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - come mandatory annotations are missing in the class
      LocalizationException - on any localization exceptions
      ContentException - on any format errors
      Since:
      0.0.4
